text: Eugénio Eleutério was a sprinter from Portugal. Eleutério competed at the 1952 Summer Olympics. He was born on 3 November 1920 and died on 28 July 2020.Eugénio Eleutério == References == Category:1920 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Sprinters Category:Olympians for Portugal Category:Portuguese athletes
